<p>纯手工皮雕画《千里江山图1》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201202/59552d5c78134a808645defb8c8501b5.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
